aroha
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:love, sympathy 1. n. Love, yearning for and absent relative or friend. ... 2. Pity, compassion. ... 3. Affectionate regard. ... 4. v.i. Feel love or pity.  5. v.t. Show approval.]  [OED2 1978 cit only at aloha: aloha 1825.] Sympathy, understanding or love
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
